<p>Ready to give up on your Mac? Don&#39;t let it go quite so easily. There might be an option or a repair or an upgrade! Have a Drobo or a DiskStation (or want one)? Do you know what it takes to manage one of those devices? It&#39;s not difficult, and John and Dave explain all that and more for you in one easy-to-digest podcast episode!</p>
